com.calendarfx.view

Enum MonthSheetView.ViewUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MonthSheetView.ViewUnit>
      • com.calendarfx.view.MonthSheetView.ViewUnit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<MonthSheetView.ViewUnit>
    Enclosing class:
    MonthSheetView

    public static enum MonthSheetView.ViewUnit
extends Enum<MonthSheetView.ViewUnit>
    A view unit describes how many months the view should show. The view knows about years, semesters (6 months), quarters (3 months), and single months. When the date property changes the view will make sure to show the year, semester, quarter, or month where that date is located.
    See Also:
    MonthSheetView.setViewUnit(ViewUnit), MonthSheetView.setExtendedViewUnit(ViewUnit)
